data.description: Welcome to Northwood Estates! This beautiful well maintained single story home is located in a quiet cul-de-sac. It features 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms and 2 living rooms each with a fireplace! Welcoming entry opens to the elegant foyer & open concept layout with high ceilings, large windows & abundant natural light. Living room seamlessly flows to formal dining creating the perfect space to entertain guests. The family room boasts a gas log fireplace creating a cozy ambiance making it ideal spot for year round enjoyment. The spacious kitchen has a gas cooktop, double ovens, large island and includes a breakfast area. The primary suite has an incredible ensuite featuring a spa like shower & amazing walk in closet. 2 spacious bedrooms on the other end of the home share a jack and jill bathroom. 3rd bedroom has its own full bathroom perfect for guests. Relax in the fully fenced backyard equipped with a water feature and screened porch.
